abstract: >
  Vector Helper is an open conceptual and architectural framework for an
  AI-based visual assistant ecosystem designed to improve accessibility,
  reduce cognitive overload, and support ethical human-centered interaction.
  This repository documents system architecture, ethical constraints,
  accessibility principles, and long-term vision rather than a finished product.

